---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const siteURL = 'https://agenteconomy.cn';

const post = {
  titleZh: 'OpenAI 发布 Workspace Agents：面向团队的共享智能体',
  titleEn: 'OpenAI introduces workspace agents in ChatGPT for team collaboration',
  date: '2026-04-22',
  tags: ['AI-Agents', 'OpenAI', 'ChatGPT', 'Workspace', 'Collaboration', 'Codex'],
  source: 'OpenAI'
};

const contentZh = `
<p>OpenAI 推出面向团队的 Workspace Agents，支持复杂任务和长期工作流。基于 Codex 构建，可在 ChatGPT 和 Slack 中协作使用，并支持按计划触发和自动执行。</p>

<h2>核心功能</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>团队协作</strong>：团队可以创建共享智能体，处理复杂任务和长期工作流</li>
<li><strong>云端运行</strong>：基于 Codex 构建，在云端运行，即使离线也能持续工作</li>
<li><strong>多平台集成</strong>：可在 ChatGPT 和 Slack 中使用，支持按计划触发</li>
<li><strong>企业级安全</strong>：提供权限控制、审批流程和合规 API</li>
</ul>

<h2>应用场景</h2>
<p>OpenAI 展示了多个实际应用案例：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>销售助手</strong>：自动研究客户、整理通话记录、起草跟进邮件</li>
<li><strong>软件审核</strong>：审核员工软件请求，对照批准工具和政策</li>
<li><strong>产品反馈路由</strong>：监控 Slack 和支持渠道，将反馈转为优先级工单</li>
<li><strong>周报生成</strong>：每周五自动拉取数据、创建图表、撰写摘要</li>
</ul>

<h2>定价与可用性</h2>
<p>Workspace Agents 目前处于研究预览阶段，面向 ChatGPT Business、Enterprise、Edu 和 Teachers 计划用户开放。在 2026 年 5 月 6 日前免费使用，之后将转为基于信用的定价模式。</p>

<p>阅读完整文章：<a href="https://openai.com/index/introducing-workspace-agents-in-chatgpt/">https://openai.com/index/introducing-workspace-agents-in-chatgpt/</a></p>
`;

const contentEn = `
<p>OpenAI introduces workspace agents in ChatGPT, enabling teams to create shared agents for complex tasks and long-running workflows. Powered by Codex, these agents can work in the cloud, integrate with Slack, and operate on schedules.</p>

<h2>Key Features</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Team Collaboration</strong>: Teams can create shared agents to handle complex tasks and long-running workflows</li>
<li><strong>Cloud-Powered</strong>: Built on Codex, running in the cloud so they keep working even when you're offline</li>
<li><strong>Multi-Platform</strong>: Available in ChatGPT and Slack, with scheduled triggers</li>
<li><strong>Enterprise Security</strong>: Permission controls, approval workflows, and compliance API</li>
</ul>

<h2>Use Cases</h2>
<p>OpenAI showcased several real-world applications:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Sales Assistant</strong>: Research accounts, summarize calls, draft follow-up emails</li>
<li><strong>Software Reviewer</strong>: Review employee software requests against approved tools and policies</li>
<li><strong>Product Feedback Router</strong>: Monitor Slack and support channels, turn feedback into prioritized tickets</li>
<li><strong>Weekly Metrics Reporter</strong>: Pull data every Friday, create charts, write summaries</li>
</ul>

<h2>Pricing & Availability</h2>
<p>Workspace Agents is currently in research preview for ChatGPT Business, Enterprise, Edu, and Teachers plans. Free until May 6, 2026, then switching to credit-based pricing.</p>

<p>Read the full article at <a href="https://openai.com/index/introducing-workspace-agents-in-chatgpt/">https://openai.com/index/introducing-workspace-agents-in-chatgpt/</a></p>
`;
---

<Layout title={post.titleZh} description={post.excerptZh}>
  <article class="blog-post">
    <header class="post-header">
      <div class="post-meta">
        <time datetime={post.date}>{post.date}</time>
        <span class="source">{post.source}</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="post-title">
        <span class="lang-content lang-zh active">{post.titleZh}</span>
        <span class="lang-content lang-en">{post.titleEn}</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="post-tags">
        {post.tags.map(tag => (
          <span class="tag">{tag}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-content">
      <div class="lang-content lang-zh active" set:html={contentZh} />
      <div class="lang-content lang-en" set:html={contentEn} />
    </div>

    <footer class="post-footer">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">
        <span class="lang-content lang-zh active">← 返回首页</span>
        <span class="lang-content lang-en">← Back to Home</span>
      </a>
    </footer>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .blog-post {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  .post-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .post-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .post-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .post-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tag {
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: var(--tag-bg);
    color: var(--tag-color);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .post-content {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .post-content :global(h2) {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .post-content :global(h3) {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .post-content :global(p) {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .post-content :global(ul) {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .post-content :global(li) {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .post-content :global(a) {
    color: var(--link-color);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .post-content :global(a:hover) {
    color: var(--link-hover-color);
  }

  .post-footer {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .post-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .post-content {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>